parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column lock can cause the steering wheel to seize or lock, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks or seizes
the service steering warning lamp illuminates
the vehicle stalls
the steering wheel unlocks after removing the key and waiting ten seconds
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls when put into gear
the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to become inoperable, making it impossible to use, which can lead to accidents or injuries in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The seat belt will not retract
the seat belt gets stuck in the out position
the seat belt binds at the corner
the seat belt will not release from the retracting mechanism
the seat belt is jammed and unusable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt ratcheting mechanism can cause the seat belt to become inoperable, making it impossible to use, which can lead to accidents or injuries in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The seat belt mechanism repeatedly jams
the seat belt is unable to lock
the seat belt twists as it retracts
the seat belt does not retract fully
the seat belt is prevented from being pulled out due to the locking mechanism.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design flaw in the seat belt system can cause the seat belt to become inoperable, making it impossible to use, which can lead to accidents or injuries in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The seat belt retractor spring is not strong enough to completely wind in the belt
the seat belt feeds into the retractor folded over
the seat belt is prevented from being pulled out due to the locking mechanism.

symptoms: Cruise control suddenly disables
uneven brake feeling
loss of ABS and traction control systems
sudden slowdown of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Randomly turning off headlights while driving can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Headlights randomly turn off while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Intermittent failure of turn signal blinkers can cause confusion to other drivers, leading to potential accidents.
symptoms: Turn signal blinkers fail to work intermittently.
